Lifecycle Methods => Mounting/Unmounting/Updating DOM
Class Component -
this.bind or use arrow function
Functional Component -
Doesn't need `this`

Three phases in React-

Mounting => Loads/Renders first time => ComponentDidMount => useEffect

Updating => Update => ComponentDidUpdate => useEffect with pararameters

Unmounting => Removing component => ComponentWillUnmount => return inside useEffect

Constructor => Used before mounting 

UseState => To change the state

To improve the performance (optimization) (Stored in cache)
UseMemo => To Memoize the value/result 
useCallback => To Memoize the function
memo(Child)
